{"tid":2308404,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"宮崎駿親筆信賀《波兒》等足12年入境大陸：波妞能帶快樂就太好啦","createTime":"2020-12-02T00:54:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-02T01:57:26.000Z","uid":364068,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"bd417f7996963a93f5e5467610d5ddf7c548b2a6","tid":2308404,"uid":364068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T00:54:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201201/ORIALV32CZG5XLG3PUA5TTUBSQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201201%2FORIALV32CZG5XLG3PUA5TTUBSQ%2F&d=TN93oS71akEChVkkxtef2QwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=f439d7a9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201201%2FORIALV32CZG5XLG3PUA5TTUBSQ%2F&h=8f7bd3d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201201/ORIALV32CZG5XLG3PUA5TTUBSQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n由日本動畫大師宮崎駿手繪畫製作的動畫片《崖上的波兒》，於2008年在日本率先上映，當年錄得155億日圓票房，成為當年的票房冠軍，電影主題曲更唱到街知巷聞，紅到當年年末上《紅白》。其後《波兒》先後在港、台、歐美等地上映。不過，當年的《波兒》無法順利取得「通行證」，故一直未能入境大陸，令大陸觀眾得個恨字。<br />\n<br />\n時間一眨眼便過了12年，近日有消息指《波兒》終獲大陸批准「入境」，並定於除夕當日在大陸戲院上映。宮崎駿日前更以親筆信做宣傳，他以中文寫上，「波妞能帶快樂，就太好啦！」並畫了一隻豬及煤炭屎鬼公仔，相信是取自比《波兒》更早打入大陸的《千與千尋》及《龍貓》中的角色。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新海誠回應《鬼滅》取代《你的名字。》 坦言不甘仍會努力<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201124/MCHR64ETLNGBXB62DROMVELJWE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201124%2FMCHR64ETLNGBXB62DROMVELJWE%2F&d=TN93oS71akEChVkkxtef2QwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=da7884e2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201124%2FMCHR64ETLNGBXB62DROMVELJWE%2F&h=c94ec146\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201124/MCHR64ETLNGBXB62DROMVELJWE/</a><br />\n<br />\n無懼票房被超車! 宮崎駿撿垃圾談《鬼滅之刃》 說：「我不會看，我現在不看電視也不看電影，我只是一個退休老人，努力撿垃圾而已。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201110/4OP44LVWTBDQXERVTWMOEOTT7U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201110%2F4OP44LVWTBDQXERVTWMOEOTT7U%2F&d=TN93oS71akEChVkkxtef2QwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=e04250ca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201110%2F4OP44LVWTBDQXERVTWMOEOTT7U%2F&h=ba266b34\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201110/4OP44LVWTBDQXERVTWMOEOTT7U/</a>"},{"pid":"16f7457cf058269a76caf4f05816e3b7e0f6953a","tid":2308404,"uid":196924,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T01:25:20.000Z","msg":"「我不會看，我現在不看電視也不看電影，我只是一個退休老人，努力撿垃圾而已。」<br />\n<br />\n你有邊次退休真係退到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"441bd1111efe16c74c8b6292aff5d6af9b0fa272","tid":2308404,"uid":38867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"16f7457cf058269a76caf4f05816e3b7e0f6953a","tid":2308404,"uid":196924,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T01:25:20.000Z","msg":"「我不會看，我現在不看電視也不看電影，我只是一個退休老人，努力撿垃圾而已。」<br />\n<br />\n你有邊次退休真係退到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T01:47:08.000Z","msg":"即係之後再有新作都係執返黎既垃圾？"},{"pid":"f3a95efeebcb51d4f2a80b0b7177616ac4506e09","tid":2308404,"uid":79793,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T01:48:11.000Z","msg":"中國式天能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3872c4e876d8bbff019f3bb0aa80483d43764c6","tid":2308404,"uid":29879,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T01:48:34.000Z","msg":"你的名字好睇好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b5d770fd543b5cb690c3a3d59348b393e2bf62c","tid":2308404,"uid":364068,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy"